Handle Text Values

Confirm that text values in a column are uniform in formatting, spelling, and language. Standardize the text strings used for dimensions to ensure proper grouping during analysis.

Use the Bucket transformation to replace similar values with a consistent value.
Fix spelling inconsistencies, such as typographical errors, plurals, uppercase and lowercase characters.
Use a column profile to review string length.
